Titolo: Balloon Bomber

Anno: 1980

Descrizione: Balloon Bomber is a fixed shooter arcade game released by Taito in 1980. The player controls a ship at the bottom of the screen which shoots at balloon-carrying bombs overhead. If a falling bomb hits the bottom of the screen, it makes a crater which cannot be moved past, limiting mobility.

Genere: Non specificato


Valutazione: N/A
